# Agent Runner

<% if @error -%>
**Error reading agent-runner stats:** <%= @error %>
<% end -%>

## Service Status

<% if @runner_stats -%>
| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Active Tasks | <%= @runner_stats["activeTasks"] %> |
| Total Tasks Processed | <%= @runner_stats["totalTasksProcessed"] %> |
| Started At | <%= @runner_stats["startedAt"] %> |
| Last Task At | <%= @runner_stats["lastTaskAt"] || "None" %> |
<% else -%>
**Agent runner is not reporting stats.** It may be offline or not yet started.
<% end -%>

## Redis Stream

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Stream Length | <%= @stream_length %> |
| Pending Messages | <%= @pending_count %> |

## Recent Task Runs

| ID | Agent | Status | Steps | Tokens | Started | Completed |
|----|-------|--------|-------|--------|---------|-----------|
<% @recent_task_runs.each do |run| -%>
| <%= run.id[0..7] %> | <%= run.ai_agent&.name %> | <%= run.status %> | <%= run.steps_count %> | <%= run.total_tokens %> | <%= run.started_at&.strftime("%H:%M:%S") %> | <%= run.completed_at&.strftime("%H:%M:%S") %> |
<% end -%>
